title: My earphone is wrong side which means the audio that suppose to hear at the right will hear left
content: I've tried reboot my phone. i've changed my dongled and i've tried using another earphone and still doesn't work. The dongle work perfectly on another phone and the earphone work perfectly on another phone .. so i know the problem is from the phone and not from the dongle or earphone
